downloadDescription: This zip file contains HTML and Microsoft Word templates that can be used to create documentation files for the Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 Help system.
detailsSection: These HTML and Microsoft Word templates can be used to create documentation files for the Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 Help system. For information about using these templates, see Templates for Help Documentation.
systemRequirementsSection: For information about the system requirements for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012, see System requirements for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click Download to save the file to your computer.
  2. Double-click the Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 Help Templates.zip file on your computer and follow the instructions on the screen to extract the files.
